Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:05.22,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,車站的站台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:10.40,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,奏響嘹亮的樂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.43,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,沉浮空落的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.61,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且借耳傾聽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.62,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,對即將刻消失的世界說—聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.28,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:36.82,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不會再相見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.36,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,命運在嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:44.66,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,突破臨界點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.57,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,界限已被清除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:50.23,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是絕對的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:52.79,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:58.67,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,末日理論不過是紙上談兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:04.09,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,從零和一的世界之初
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:07.92,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,吶喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:18.09,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺即將與你相見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:22.17,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我閉上雙眼
